text: Gongrospermum is a monotypic plant genus of Sapindaceae endemic to the Philippines, on Luzon. It only contains one species: Gongrospermum philippinense. ==References== Category:Endemic flora of the Philippines Category:Flora of Luzon Category:Critically endangered flora of Asia Category:Monotypic Sapindaceae genera Category:Sapindaceae Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
